  "body": "While I've been experimenting with `helm` I've tried the following and ended up in a broken state:\n\n```\nhelm install mychart-1.0.0 --name myrelease\nhelm delete myrelease\nhelm install otherchart-1.0.0 --name myrelease --replace\n```\n\nThe resources from `otherchart` are installed successfully - they are up and running in kubernetes - but `helm` insists that `myrelease` is still deleted. Because of this `helm` will ignore any further attempts to delete `myrelease`.\n",
